/-- **Phase E2 вҖ” `_auto` wrapper for the PSL(2, в„қ) FD decomposition.**

Drops the practical caller burden from `Gamma_p_Оұ_PSL_R_FD_finite_index_decomp`
by relying on the in-scope instance `Gamma_p_Оұ_image_PSL_R_quotient_countable`
(Phase E1 companion) to fill the `[Countable вҖҰ]` instance argument; the
conclusion is identical.  Downstream callers can use this `_auto` form
without staging their own `Countable` instance per call site. -/
theorem Gamma_p_Оұ_PSL_R_FD_finite_index_decomp_auto
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„ҡ) :
    IsFundamentalDomain
      (((Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R).subgroupOf
        ((Gamma1 N).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R))
      (вӢғ q : ((Gamma1 N).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R) в§ё
              (((Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R).subgroupOf
                ((Gamma1 N).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R)),
        ((q.out : ((Gamma1 N).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R)) : PSL(2, в„қ))вҒ»В№ вҖў
          Gamma1_fundDomain_PSL N)
      Ој_hyp :=
