/-- **Phase M (a) вҖ” `image_Gamma_p_Оұ_PSL Оұ` has finite index in `PSL(2, в„Ө)`.**

The image of a finite-index subgroup under a surjective hom has finite index;
applied to the surjection `SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* PSL(2, в„Ө)` and the finite-index witness
`Gamma_p_Оұ_finiteIndex`. -/
instance image_Gamma_p_Оұ_PSL_finiteIndex (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„ҡ) :
    (image_Gamma_p_Оұ_PSL (N := N) Оұ).FiniteIndex := by
  haveI : (Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ).FiniteIndex :=
    Gamma_p_Оұ_finiteIndex (N := N) Оұ
