/-- **Phase M (b) вҖ” SLвҶ’PSL fiber-sum reindexing for О“_p(Оұ)-invariant integrands.**

Mirror of `sum_SL_tile_eq_fiberwise_PSL_tile` (`PeterssonLevelN.lean:1099`)
