/-- **Phase M (b) вҖ” pairwise AE-disjointness of canonical PSL coset tiles for О“_p(Оұ).**

Analog of `aedisjoint_PSL_coset_tiles` (`PeterssonLevelN.lean:549`) at
H = image_Gamma_p_Оұ_PSL.  Uses `isFundamentalDomain_fdo_PSL.aedisjoint`
