the smaller subgroup `О“_p(Оұ)`.  The fiber count
`slToPslQuot_fiberCard_Gamma_p_Оұ Оұ` is the natural ВұI-quotient factor for
`SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё О“_p(Оұ) вҶ’ PSL(2, в„Ө) в§ё image_О“_p(Оұ)_PSL`; it is `1` when
`-I вҲҲ О“_p(Оұ)` and `2` otherwise (matching `slToPslQuot_fiberCard N` since
`-I вҲҲ О“_p(Оұ) вҶ” -I вҲҲ О“вӮҒ(N)`). -/
theorem setIntegral_Gamma_p_Оұ_fundDomain_PSL_canonical_eq_SL_outer_q_sum
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„ҡ) (h : в„Қ вҶ’ в„Ӯ)
    (h_inv : вҲҖ Оі вҲҲ Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ, вҲҖ П„ : в„Қ, h (Оі вҖў П„) = h П„)
    (h_int : IntegrableOn h
      (Gamma_p_Оұ_fundDomain_PSL_canonical (N := N) Оұ) Ој_hyp) :
    вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ,
      вҲ« П„ in (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ), h П„ вҲӮОј_hyp =
    (slToPslQuot_fiberCard_Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ) вҖў
      вҲ« П„ in Gamma_p_Оұ_fundDomain_PSL_canonical (N := N) Оұ, h П„ вҲӮОј_hyp := by
