/-- **Phase M (c) вҖ” `О“_p(Оұ)`-invariance lifts to `(О“_p(Оұ)).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R`-invariance.**

For any `О“_p(Оұ)`-invariant `h : в„Қ вҶ’ в„Ӯ` (under the SL(2, в„Ө)-action) and any
element `g` of the PSL(2, в„қ)-subgroup `(О“_p(Оұ)).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R`, the
action `g вҖў П„` factors through some SL(2, в„Ө)-element `Оі вҲҲ О“_p(Оұ)` whose
MГ¶bius action on в„Қ matches `g`'s.  The invariance hypothesis on the SL
side then transfers to `g`. -/
theorem inv_under_Gamma_p_Оұ_PSL_R_of_inv_under_Gamma_p_Оұ
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„ҡ) {h : в„Қ вҶ’ в„Ӯ}
    (h_inv : вҲҖ Оі вҲҲ Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ, вҲҖ П„ : в„Қ, h (Оі вҖў П„) = h П„)
    (g : ((Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R)) (П„ : в„Қ) :
    h (g вҖў П„) = h П„ := by
  obtain вҹЁОі, hОі_mem, hОі_eqвҹ© := g.property
  have h_smul : (g : PSL(2, в„қ)) вҖў П„ = Оі вҖў П„ := by
    rw [вҶҗ hОі_eq, SL2Z_to_PSL2R_smul]
    -- Remaining goal: `(SpecialLinearGroup.map (Int.castRingHom в„қ)) Оі вҖў П„ = Оі вҖў П„`.
    -- The SL(2, в„Ө) action on в„Қ factors through SL(2, в„қ) via `Int.castRingHom в„қ`,
    -- so the two sides are definitionally equal (`sl_moeb` is `rfl`).
    rfl
  show h ((g : PSL(2, в„қ)) вҖў П„) = h П„
  rw [h_smul]
  exact h_inv Оі hОі_mem П„

