/-- **Phase M (c) вҖ” countability of the PSL(2, в„қ)-side image of `О“_p(Оұ)`.**

`(О“_p(Оұ)).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R` is a countable set: it is the image of the
countable group `О“_p(Оұ) вүӨ SL(2, в„Ө)` under the hom `SL2Z_to_PSL2R`.

The proof exhibits the surjective map `О“_p(Оұ) вҶ’ (О“_p(Оұ)).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R`
sending `Оі вҶҰ вҹЁSL2Z_to_PSL2R Оі.val, вҹЁОі.val, Оі.property, rflвҹ©вҹ©`; surjectivity
+ `Function.Surjective.countable` from countability of `О“_p(Оұ)` (which is
countable as a subgroup of the countable `SL(2, в„Ө)`) gives the conclusion.
Required by `IsFundamentalDomain.setIntegral_eq` below. -/
instance Gamma_p_Оұ_PSL_R_countable
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„ҡ) :
    Countable ((Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R) := by
  classical
  let F : Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ вҶ’
      ((Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ).map SL2Z_to_PSL2R) :=
    fun Оі => вҹЁSL2Z_to_PSL2R (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)),
      вҹЁ(Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)), Оі.property, rflвҹ©вҹ©
  exact Function.Surjective.countable (f := F) (by
    intro g
    rcases g.property with вҹЁОі, hОі, hОі_eqвҹ©
    refine вҹЁвҹЁОі, hОівҹ©, ?_вҹ©
    exact Subtype.ext hОі_eq)

