open CongruenceSubgroup UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **Phase M (f) вҖ” Petersson kernel: `О“_p(Оұ)` outer-SL sum equals `relIndex вҖў petN`.**

For two `О“вӮҒ(N)`-cusp forms `f, g`, the SL outer-quotient sum over the
`О“_p(Оұ)` quotient of `petersson k вҮ‘f вҮ‘g` integrals over `q.outвҒ»В№ вҖў fd` tiles
equals `slGamma_p_ОұToGamma1_fiberCard Оұ` (= `[О“вӮҒ(N) : О“_p(Оұ)]`) times
`petN f g`:
```
вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё О“_p(Оұ), вҲ«_{q.outвҒ»В№ вҖў fd} petersson k вҮ‘f вҮ‘g dОј_hyp
  = (slGamma_p_ОұToGamma1_fiberCard Оұ) вҖў petN f g.
```

Direct consumer of `sum_SL_tile_Gamma_p_Оұ_eq_fiberCard_mul_SL_tile_Gamma1`
(Phase M(e), at `h := petersson k вҮ‘f вҮ‘g` with the О“вӮҒ(N)-invariance hypothesis
discharged via `petersson_Gamma1_invariant`).  Recognises the resulting
SL/О“вӮҒ(N) sum as the standard `petN f g` definition, via per-q
`petN_summand_eq_setIntegral`.

**Use site (T205 Hecke-adjoint chain).**  The right form for downstream
consumers that aggregate the SL outer-q sums over the О“_p(Оұ) coset family
into the standard `petN`-level statement: the integral-side picks up
`relIndex` copies of the level-`N` Petersson `petN`, with no further FD
transport. -/
theorem sum_SL_Gamma_p_Оұ_setIntegral_fd_petersson_eq_relIndex_mul_petN
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„ҡ) (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k) :
    вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma_p_Оұ (N := N) Оұ,
      вҲ« П„ in (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ),
        petersson k вҮ‘f вҮ‘g П„ вҲӮОј_hyp =
    (slGamma_p_ОұToGamma1_fiberCard (N := N) Оұ) вҖў petN f g := by
  rw [sum_SL_tile_Gamma_p_Оұ_eq_fiberCard_mul_SL_tile_Gamma1 (N := N) Оұ
      (petersson k вҮ‘f вҮ‘g)
      (fun Оі hОі П„ => petersson_Gamma1_invariant f g Оі hОі П„)]
  -- Recognise вҲ‘ q' : SL/О“вӮҒ(N), вҲ«_{q'.outвҒ»В№ вҖў fd} petersson f g as petN f g.
  congr 1
  show вҲ‘ q' : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      вҲ« П„ in (q'.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ),
        petersson k вҮ‘f вҮ‘g П„ вҲӮОј_hyp = petN f g
  unfold petN
  refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q' _ => ?_
  exact (petN_summand_eq_setIntegral f g q').symm

