/-- **Phase M (g) prelude вҖ” generic SL-element petersson-fd-slash setIntegral identity.**

Generic-`s : SL(2, в„Ө)` analog of `peterssonInner_fd_slash_q_eq_setIntegral_shifted_fd`:
the per-q lemma whose proof depends only on `q.out : SL(2, в„Ө)` extracted to take a
direct SL element.  Same proof structure as Phase L(a): unfold `peterssonInner`,
rewrite via `petersson_slash_SL`, then apply change of variables. -/
theorem peterssonInner_fd_slash_SL_eq_setIntegral_shifted_fd
    (F G : в„Қ вҶ’ в„Ӯ) (s : SL(2, в„Ө)) :
    peterssonInner k fd (F вҲЈ[k] (s : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) (G вҲЈ[k] (s : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) =
