/-- **Phase M (g) вҖ” Petersson kernel: `О“_p(Оұ)` outer-SL `petN`-summand sum equals `relIndex вҖў petN`.**

`petN`-summand variant of Phase M (f) (`sum_SL_Gamma_p_Оұ_setIntegral_fd_petersson_eq_relIndex_mul_petN`):
the SL outer-quotient sum over `SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё О“_p(Оұ)` of the per-`q` `peterssonInner k fd
(вҮ‘f вҲЈ[k] q.outвҒ»В№) (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] q.outвҒ»В№)` summands equals `(slGamma_p_ОұToGamma1_fiberCard Оұ)
