/-- **T024 aggregate per-Оұ slash-adjoint at the О“вӮҒ(N)-FD level**.

Sum-level aggregation of `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset` over the
`SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N` quotient: the per-q-per-Оұ slash-adjoint identity,
summed over q, collapses (via `peterssonInner_iUnion_finite_aedisjoint`)
to a single Petersson integral over the ОІ-shifted О“вӮҒ(N) fundamental
domain `вӢғ_q (ОІ В· mapGL q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd`.

**Mathematical content (sum-level absorbed-RHS route).**  This provides
content (A) of the per-Оұ residual reduction described in
`petN_LHS_dist_eq_RHS_absorbed_from_two_residuals`'s docstring: the
per-Оұ aggregate slash-adjoint at the О“вӮҒ(N)-FD level. Combined with the
matrix-coset bijection `peterssonAdj Оұ вҶ” Оұ^*` modulo О“вӮҒ(N) (content
(B)), it discharges the per-Оұ residual via Hecke double-coset matching.

**Inputs.**  Caller supplies:
* `hОІ : 0 < ОІ.det.val` (ОІ has positive determinant);
* `hd : Pairwise AEDisjoint` of the ОІ-shifted О“вӮҒ(N) tile family
  (from existing AE-disjoint helpers like
  `aedisjoint_glMap_M_infty_T_p_upper`,
  `aedisjoint_glMap_T_p_upper_pair_fd_per_q` for specific ОІ);
* `hm : NullMeasurable` of each tile;
* `hint : IntegrableOn` of `petersson k F (G вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj ОІ)` on
  the union.

**Use site (DS 5.5.2(b)).**  Apply with ОІ = `glMap M_вҲһ` for the M_вҲһ
residual reduction or ОІ = `glMap T_p_upper(b)` for the upper-b residual
reduction; supply the AE-disjoint and integrability hypotheses from the
existing per-tile helpers landed in this file. -/
theorem peterssonInner_sum_slash_adjoint_coset_aggregate
    (ОІ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) (hОІ : 0 < ОІ.det.val)
    (F G : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ)
    (hd : Pairwise (fun (qвӮҒ qвӮӮ : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N) =>
      AEDisjoint Ој_hyp
        ((ОІ * (mapGL в„қ (qвӮҒ.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
        ((ОІ * (mapGL в„қ (qвӮӮ.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў fd)))
    (hm : вҲҖ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      NullMeasurableSet
        ((ОІ * (mapGL в„қ (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ)) Ој_hyp)
    (hint : IntegrableOn (fun П„ => petersson k F (G вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj ОІ) П„)
      (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        (ОІ * (mapGL в„қ (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ)) Ој_hyp) :
    (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (F вҲЈ[k] (ОІ * (mapGL в„қ (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
        (G вҲЈ[k] (mapGL в„қ (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
    peterssonInner k
      (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        (ОІ * (mapGL в„қ (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
      F (G вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj ОІ) := by
  rw [show (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (F вҲЈ[k] (ОІ * (mapGL в„қ (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
          (G вҲЈ[k] (mapGL в„қ (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
      вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k
          ((ОІ * (mapGL в„қ (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
          F (G вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj ОІ) from by
    refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
    rw [peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset (k := k) ОІ hОІ
      (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө)) F G, вҶҗ mul_smul]]
  exact (peterssonInner_iUnion_finite_aedisjoint
    (fun q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N =>
      (ОІ * (mapGL в„қ (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
    hm hd F (G вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj ОІ) hint).symm

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T106 helper: `glMap M_вҲһ` has positive determinant `p` in `GL (Fin 2) в„қ`.** -/
theorem glMap_M_infty_det_pos
    (N p : в„•) [NeZero N] (hp : 0 < p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N) :
    0 < (glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ).det.val := by
  show 0 < ((glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
    Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ).det
  rw [show ((glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
      Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ) =
      ((M_infty N p hp hpN : GL (Fin 2) в„ҡ).val).map (algebraMap в„ҡ в„қ) from rfl]
  rw [show (((M_infty N p hp hpN : GL (Fin 2) в„ҡ).val).map (algebraMap в„ҡ в„қ)).det =
    (algebraMap в„ҡ в„қ) (((M_infty N p hp hpN : GL (Fin 2) в„ҡ).val).det) from
      (RingHom.map_det _ _).symm]
  -- det(M_вҲһ) in GL(Fin 2) в„ҡ equals p (since M_вҲһ has det p by construction).
  have h_det_Q : ((M_infty N p hp hpN : GL (Fin 2) в„ҡ).val).det = (p : в„ҡ) := by
    have hmem := N_mul_mIdx_eq N p hpN
    simp only [M_infty_val, Matrix.det_fin_two_of]
    have hmem_q : ((N : в„Ө) * mIdxOfCoprime N p hpN : в„ҡ) =
        (aInvOfCoprime N p hpN : в„Ө) * p - 1 := by exact_mod_cast hmem
    rw [hmem_q]
    ring
  rw [h_det_Q]
  show 0 < (algebraMap в„ҡ в„қ) ((p : в„ҡ))
  rw [show (algebraMap в„ҡ в„қ) ((p : в„ҡ)) = ((p : в„ҡ) : в„қ) from rfl]
  exact_mod_cast hp

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T128 per-`q` M_вҲһ vs T_p_upper(b) fd-AE-disjoint helper**.

For the Option `(Fin p)` family at fixed `q : SL(2, в„Ө)`, the `none` tile
`(glMap M_вҲһ В· mapGL qвҒ»В№) вҖў fd` is AE-disjoint from each `some b` tile
`(glMap T_p_upper(b) В· mapGL qвҒ»В№) вҖў fd`.

**Uses**: `aedisjoint_glMap_smul_fd_of_mul_inv_eq_mapGL_PSL_ne` with
`Пғ = q В· M_infty_Gamma1_factor(b)вҒ»В№ В· qвҒ»В№`, `h_inv_mul` from
`glMap_T_p_upper_inv_mul_M_infty_eq_mapGL_Gamma1` (reversed + conjugated),
PSL nontriviality from `M_infty_Gamma1_factor_psl_ne_one` preserved under
conjugation by `q`. -/
theorem aedisjoint_glMap_M_infty_T_p_upper_fd_per_q
    {N : в„•} [NeZero N] {p : в„•} (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (q : SL(2, в„Ө)) (b : в„•) :
    AEDisjoint Ој_hyp
      (((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
        ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў
          (ModularGroup.fd : Set в„Қ))
      (((glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
        ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў
          (ModularGroup.fd : Set в„Қ)) := by
  set ОұвӮҒ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ :=
    (glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
      ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
  set ОұвӮӮ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ :=
    (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
      ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
  have h_mapGL_mat_det_eq_one :
      (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
        Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ).det = 1 := by
    rw [show (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
        Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ) =
        ((Int.castRingHom в„қ).mapMatrix (qвҒ»В№ : SL(2, в„Ө)).val) by
      rw [mapGL_coe_matrix]; rfl]
    rw [вҶҗ RingHom.map_det, (qвҒ»В№ : SL(2, в„Ө)).property]
    simp
  have h_ОұвӮҒ_det_pos : 0 < (ОұвӮҒ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ).det.val := by
    show 0 < ((ОұвӮҒ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) : Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ).det
    rw [show ((ОұвӮҒ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) : Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ) =
        ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
          Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ) *
        (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
          Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ) from Units.val_mul _ _,
      Matrix.det_mul, h_mapGL_mat_det_eq_one, mul_one]
    exact glMap_M_infty_det_pos N p hp.pos hpN
  have h_ОұвӮҒ_inv_det_pos : 0 < (ОұвӮҒвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ).det.val := by
    show 0 < (((ОұвӮҒвҒ»В№).det : в„қЛЈ) : в„қ)
    rw [show ((ОұвӮҒвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)).det = ОұвӮҒ.detвҒ»В№ from map_inv _ _,
      Units.val_inv_eq_inv_val]
    exact inv_pos.mpr h_ОұвӮҒ_det_pos
  have h_inv_mul : ОұвӮҒвҒ»В№ * ОұвӮӮ =
      ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
        (q * (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b)вҒ»В№ * qвҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) := by
    show (((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))вҒ»В№ *
        ((glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) = _
    rw [mul_inv_rev]
    rw [show (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))вҒ»В№ =
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) q : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) from by
        rw [вҶҗ map_inv]; simp]
    have h_inv_mul_M_infty :
        ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))вҒ»В№ *
          (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) =
        ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b))вҒ»В№ := by
      have h :=
        glMap_T_p_upper_inv_mul_M_infty_eq_mapGL_Gamma1 N p hp.pos hpN b
      rw [show ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b))вҒ»В№ =
          ((glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)вҒ»В№ *
            (glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))вҒ»В№ from by rw [h]]
      rw [mul_inv_rev, inv_inv]
    rw [mul_assoc ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) q : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)вҒ»В№,
      вҶҗ mul_assoc ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))вҒ»В№
          (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ),
      h_inv_mul_M_infty,
      вҶҗ mul_assoc,
      вҶҗ map_inv, вҶҗ map_mul, вҶҗ map_mul]
  have h_psl_factor_ne :
      (QuotientGroup.mk (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b) : PSL(2, в„Ө)) вү  1 :=
    M_infty_Gamma1_factor_psl_ne_one N p hp hpN b
  have h_psl_factor_inv_ne :
      (QuotientGroup.mk (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b)вҒ»В№ : PSL(2, в„Ө)) вү  1 := by
    intro heq
    apply h_psl_factor_ne
    rw [QuotientGroup.mk_inv] at heq
    exact inv_eq_one.mp heq
  have h_psl_conj_ne :
      (QuotientGroup.mk (q * (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b)вҒ»В№ * qвҒ»В№) :
        PSL(2, в„Ө)) вү  1 := by
    intro heq
    apply h_psl_factor_inv_ne
    have hconj : (QuotientGroup.mk q : PSL(2, в„Ө)) *
            (QuotientGroup.mk (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b)вҒ»В№ : PSL(2, в„Ө)) *
            (QuotientGroup.mk q : PSL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ = 1 := by
      rw [вҶҗ QuotientGroup.mk_inv, вҶҗ QuotientGroup.mk_mul, вҶҗ QuotientGroup.mk_mul]
      exact heq
    rw [mul_inv_eq_one] at hconj
    exact mul_left_cancel (hconj.trans (mul_one _).symm)
  exact aedisjoint_glMap_smul_fd_of_mul_inv_eq_mapGL_PSL_ne ОұвӮҒ ОұвӮӮ
    (measurePreserving_glPos_smul _ h_ОұвӮҒ_inv_det_pos)
    (q * (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b)вҒ»В№ * qвҒ»В№)
    h_psl_conj_ne h_inv_mul

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T106 right-slash M_вҲһ adjoint coset identity**: per-`q` M_вҲһ-summand
transformation for the Hecke adjoint.

Composes `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset` (at ОІ = glMap M_вҲһ) with
`peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq` to rewrite the `g`-side adjoint-slash in a
clean form suitable for the right-slash T205 closure path. The resulting
RHS integrand is `g вҲЈ[k] (glMap T_p_upper(0) * mapGL в„қ Пғ_pвҒ»В№)`, which on
a cusp form further simplifies via the matrix identity `T_p_upper(0) В· Пғ_pвҒ»В№
= p В· M_вҲһвҒ»В№` (not used here вҖ” kept in this compiled form for flexibility). -/
theorem peterssonInner_M_infty_slash_adjoint_coset
    (N p : в„•) [NeZero N] (hp : 0 < p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (q : SL(2, в„Ө)) (f g : в„Қ вҶ’ в„Ӯ) :
    peterssonInner k fd
        (f вҲЈ[k] ((glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
          (mapGL в„қ qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
        (g вҲЈ[k] (mapGL в„қ qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) =
      peterssonInner k
        ((glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў
          ((mapGL в„қ qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ)))
        f
        (g вҲЈ[k] ((glMap (T_p_upper p hp 0) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) (sigma_p_specific N p hp hpN)вҒ»В№))) := by
  rw [peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset
      (glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN)) (glMap_M_infty_det_pos N p hp hpN) q f g]
  rw [peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq N p hp hpN]

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T126 coset-reindex helper (cusp-form version)**: for a `О“вӮҒ(N)`-cusp
form `g` and `Оі вҲҲ О“вӮҖ(N)`, slashing by `(Пғ q).outвҒ»В№` where
`Пғ = Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 Оі` equals slashing by `q.outвҒ»В№` after applying
the diamond operator `вҹЁGamma0MapUnits Оівҹ©`.

Captures the core "О“вӮҖ(N)-coset-reindex absorbs into diamond shift" identity:
under the `q вҶҰ qВ·ОівҒ»В№` reindex of `SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё О“вӮҒ(N)`, the slashed cusp form
`g вҲЈ[k] (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№` collapses to `(вҹЁGamma0MapUnits Оівҹ© g) вҲЈ[k] q.outвҒ»В№`.

**Role in T205 closure.**  This is the precise sub-lemma missing for the
`q вҶҰ qВ·ОівӮҖвҒ»В№` reindex in `petN_heckeT_p_diamond_shift_core`: applied at
Оі = `adjointGamma0Rep` (so `Gamma0MapUnits Оі = uвҒ»В№`), we get the identity
`g вҲЈ (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№ = (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ© g) вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№` for О“вӮҒ(N)-cusp forms on the
"outer" `g` slot of `peterssonInner k fd (В· вҲЈ qвҒ»В№) (g вҲЈ qвҒ»В№)`.

**Proof.**  By definition of `Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0`, `(Пғ q) = вҹҰq.outВ·ОівҒ»В№вҹ§`
in `SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё О“вӮҒ(N)`.  Extract `О·вӮҖ вҲҲ О“вӮҒ(N)` with
`(Пғ q).out = q.out В· ОівҒ»В№ В· О·вӮҖвҒ»В№`; then `(Пғ q).outвҒ»В№ = О·вӮҖ В· Оі В· q.outвҒ»В№`.
Using `slash_Gamma1_eq` to absorb `О·вӮҖ` and `diamondOpCusp_eq` to identify
`g вҲЈ Оі` with `вҹЁGamma0MapUnits Оівҹ© g`, the identity follows. -/
theorem slash_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq_diamond_slash_out_inv
    (Оі : вҶҘ(Gamma0 N)) (g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k)
    (q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N) :
    вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) Оі.property q).out :
      SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ =
    вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (Gamma0MapUnits Оі) g) вҲЈ[k]
      (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ := by
  -- Step 1: extract О·вӮҖ вҲҲ О“вӮҒ(N) with (Пғ q).out = q.out В· ОівҒ»В№ В· О·вӮҖвҒ»В№.
  set Пғ := Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) Оі.property
  have h_coset_eq : (Пғ q) = вҹҰq.out * (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№вҹ§ := by
    conv_lhs => rw [show q = вҹҰq.outвҹ§ from q.out_eq.symm]
    rfl
  have h_out_eq_mk : вҹҰ(Пғ q).outвҹ§ = (вҹҰq.out * (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№вҹ§ :
      SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N) := by
    rw [вҶҗ h_coset_eq, (Пғ q).out_eq]
  have h_mem : ((Пғ q).out)вҒ»В№ * (q.out * (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) вҲҲ Gamma1 N := by
    have h_left_rel := Quotient.exact h_out_eq_mk
    change (QuotientGroup.leftRel _).r _ _ at h_left_rel
    rwa [QuotientGroup.leftRel_apply] at h_left_rel
  set О·вӮҖ := ((Пғ q).out)вҒ»В№ * (q.out * (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)
  -- Step 2: `(Пғ q).out = q.out В· ОівҒ»В№ В· О·вӮҖвҒ»В№`, so `(Пғ q).outвҒ»В№ = О·вӮҖ В· Оі В· q.outвҒ»В№`.
  have h_inv_eq : ((Пғ q).out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ =
      О·вӮҖ * (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) * ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө)))вҒ»В№ := by
    show ((Пғ q).out)вҒ»В№ = О·вӮҖ * (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) * (q.out)вҒ»В№
    show ((Пғ q).out)вҒ»В№ = (((Пғ q).out)вҒ»В№ * (q.out * (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)) *
        (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) * (q.out)вҒ»В№
    group
  rw [h_inv_eq, SlashAction.slash_mul, SlashAction.slash_mul]
  -- Step 3: slash by О·вӮҖ вҲҲ О“вӮҒ(N) is identity on cusp form g.
  rw [show вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] О·вӮҖ = вҮ‘g from
    SlashInvariantFormClass.slash_action_eq g _
      (Subgroup.mem_map.mpr вҹЁО·вӮҖ, h_mem, rflвҹ©)]
  -- Step 4: slash by Оі вҲҲ О“вӮҖ(N) is diamond operator on cusp form g.
  rw [show вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) =
    вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (Gamma0MapUnits Оі) g) from by
    show вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] (mapGL в„қ (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) = _
    show вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] (mapGL в„қ (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) =
      вҮ‘(diamondOpCusp k (Gamma0MapUnits Оі) g)
    rw [diamondOpCusp_eq k (Gamma0MapUnits Оі) Оі rfl]
    rfl]

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T128 Hecke-diamond whole-cusp-form coset-reindex helper**: for a
`О“вӮҒ(N)`-cusp form `g` and `Оі вҲҲ О“вӮҖ(N)`, slashing the full `T_p`-image
`heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g` by `(Пғ q).outвҒ»В№` (where
`Пғ = Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 Оі`) equals slashing
`heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN (вҹЁGamma0MapUnits Оівҹ© g)` by `q.outвҒ»В№`.

Composes T126 (`slash_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq_diamond_slash_out_inv`)
with `heckeT_p_comm_diamondOp` (the `ModularForm`-level Hecke/diamond
commutation) to push the diamond twist inside `T_p_cusp` at function level.

**Role in T205 closure.** The `q вҶҰ qВ·ОівӮҖвҒ»В№` reindex on the
`heckeT_p_cusp g` side is absorbed into a single diamond twist of `g`,
simultaneously covering BOTH residual non-invariant slash terms of the
naive double-coset decomposition вҖ” the upper-ut sum
`heckeT_p_ut k p hp.pos вҮ‘g` and the `M_вҲһ` piece
`вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] M_вҲһ` вҖ” since they are the two components of the single quantity
`heckeT_p_cusp g вҲЈ[k] (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№`.  This sidesteps the per-`b`
permutation/conjugation route (which fails because the naive matrix
conjugate `T_p_upper(b) В· ОівӮҖ В· T_p_upper(b)вҒ»В№` has non-integer entries
in general). -/
theorem slash_heckeT_p_cusp_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (Оі : вҶҘ(Gamma0 N)) (g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k)
    (q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N) :
    вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g) вҲЈ[k]
      ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) Оі.property q).out :
        SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ =
    вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN
        (diamondOp_cusp k (Gamma0MapUnits Оі) g)) вҲЈ[k]
      (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ := by
  -- Step 1: apply T126 helper to `heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g`.
  rw [slash_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq_diamond_slash_out_inv Оі
      (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g) q]
  set d := Gamma0MapUnits Оі with hd_def
  -- Goal: вҮ‘(вҹЁdвҹ©_cusp (T_p_cusp g)) вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№ = вҮ‘(T_p_cusp (вҹЁdвҹ©_cusp g)) вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№
  -- Reduce to equality of the underlying functions.
  suffices h_eq : (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k d (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g)) :
      UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) =
      вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN (diamondOp_cusp k d g)) by
    rw [h_eq]
  -- Step 2: diamondOp_cusp at function level is slash by Оі.
  have h_diamond_cusp_coe : вҲҖ (f : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k),
      (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k d f) : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) =
      (вҮ‘f : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) вҲЈ[k]
        (mapGL в„қ (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) := fun f => by
    show (вҮ‘(diamondOpCusp k d f) : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) = _
    rw [diamondOpCusp_eq k d Оі rfl]
    rfl
  -- Step 3: diamondOp (ModularForm) at function level is slash by Оі.
  have h_diamond_mf_coe : вҲҖ (F : ModularForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k),
      (вҮ‘(diamondOp k d F) : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) =
      (вҮ‘F : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) вҲЈ[k]
        (mapGL в„қ (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) := fun F => by
    rw [diamondOp_eq_diamondOpAux k d Оі rfl]
    rfl
  -- Step 4: heckeT_p commutes with diamondOp (ModularForm level), applied to g.toModularForm'.
  have h_comm_app : diamondOp k d (heckeT_p k p hp hpN g.toModularForm') =
      heckeT_p k p hp hpN (diamondOp k d g.toModularForm') :=
    LinearMap.congr_fun
      (heckeT_p_comm_diamondOp (N := N) k p hp hpN d) g.toModularForm'
  -- Step 5: heckeT_p's value (as a function) depends only on вҮ‘F (via heckeT_p_fun_eq_coset_sum).
  have h_heckeT_p_congr : вҲҖ (FвӮҒ FвӮӮ : ModularForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k),
      (вҮ‘FвӮҒ : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) = вҮ‘FвӮӮ вҶ’
      (вҮ‘(heckeT_p k p hp hpN FвӮҒ) : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) =
      вҮ‘(heckeT_p k p hp hpN FвӮӮ) := fun FвӮҒ FвӮӮ hF => by
    show heckeT_p_fun k p hp hpN FвӮҒ = heckeT_p_fun k p hp hpN FвӮӮ
    rw [heckeT_p_fun_eq_coset_sum k hp hpN FвӮҒ,
      heckeT_p_fun_eq_coset_sum k hp hpN FвӮӮ, hF]
  -- Step 6: chain the equalities.
  calc (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k d (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g)) :
        UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ)
      = (вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g) : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) вҲЈ[k]
          (mapGL в„қ (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) := h_diamond_cusp_coe _
    _ = (вҮ‘(heckeT_p k p hp hpN g.toModularForm') : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) вҲЈ[k]
          (mapGL в„қ (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) := rfl
    _ = вҮ‘(diamondOp k d (heckeT_p k p hp hpN g.toModularForm')) :=
          (h_diamond_mf_coe _).symm
    _ = вҮ‘(heckeT_p k p hp hpN (diamondOp k d g.toModularForm')) := by
          rw [h_comm_app]
    _ = вҮ‘(heckeT_p k p hp hpN (diamondOp_cusp k d g).toModularForm') := by
          apply h_heckeT_p_congr
          rw [h_diamond_mf_coe, show (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k d g).toModularForm' :
            UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) = вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k d g) from rfl,
            h_diamond_cusp_coe]
          rfl
    _ = вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN (diamondOp_cusp k d g)) := rfl

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T128 petN-level q-reindex consumer**: applying the T128 pointwise
identity across the full `вҲ‘_q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё О“вӮҒ(N)` sum (via `Equiv.sum_comp`
on `Пғ = Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 Оі`, combined with T128 on the first
`peterssonInner` slot and T126 on the second) collapses to a `petN`
identity:
`petN (T_p f) g = petN (T_p (вҹЁGamma0MapUnits Оівҹ© f)) (вҹЁGamma0MapUnits Оівҹ© g)`
for any `Оі вҲҲ О“вӮҖ(N)` and О“вӮҒ(N)-cusp forms `f, g`.

This consumer transforms a concrete `petN (T_p f) g` expression into
another `petN` expression whose arguments carry a symmetric diamond
twist вҖ” a tangible q-sum/petN reshape, not a pointwise restatement.

**Role in T205.** Specialized at `Оі = adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN` (with
`Gamma0MapUnits Оі = uвҒ»В№` via `adjointGamma0Rep_units`), it gives
`petN (T_p f) g = petN (T_p (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ© f)) (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ© g)`, which is the exact
Пғ-reindex form that appears in the T205 residual after the `ОівӮҖ`-slash
simplification path.

**Proof route.** `petN` unfolds to a `вҲ‘_q` of `peterssonInner` on
slashed cusp forms. Reindexing `q вҶҰ Пғ q` via `Equiv.sum_comp Пғ` shifts
each summand to use `(Пғ q).outвҒ»В№`. T128 absorbs the Пғ-shift on the
first `T_p_cusp f` slot and T126 absorbs it on the second `g` slot,
both yielding `q.outвҒ»В№` slashes on diamond-twisted cusp forms. -/
theorem petN_heckeT_p_Gamma1QuotEquiv_reindex
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (Оі : вҶҘ(Gamma0 N)) (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k) :
    petN (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN f) g =
      petN (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN
              (diamondOp_cusp k (Gamma0MapUnits Оі) f))
           (diamondOp_cusp k (Gamma0MapUnits Оі) g) := by
  -- Unfold `petN` on both sides to `вҲ‘_q peterssonInner ...` form.
  show вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN f) вҲЈ[k] (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)
          (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) =
      вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN
             (diamondOp_cusp k (Gamma0MapUnits Оі) f)) вҲЈ[k]
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)
          (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (Gamma0MapUnits Оі) g) вҲЈ[k]
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)
  -- Reindex the LHS sum by q вҶҰ Пғ q via `Equiv.sum_comp Пғ`.
  rw [вҶҗ Equiv.sum_comp (Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 (Оі : SL(2, в„Ө)) Оі.property)
    (fun q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N =>
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN f) вҲЈ[k] (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)
        (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№))]
  -- Apply T128 (first slot) and T126 (second slot) pointwise.
  refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
  rw [slash_heckeT_p_cusp_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq p hp hpN Оі f q,
    slash_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq_diamond_slash_out_inv Оі g q]

/-- **T128 specialization at `adjointGamma0Rep`**: the T128-based
q-reindex consumer applied at `Оі = adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN`, yielding
a symmetric `вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©`-twist form:
`petN (T_p f) g = petN (T_p (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ© f)) (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ© g)`.

This is the concrete T205 q-sum/petN residual consumer that uses the
T128 helper at the adjoint О“вӮҖ(N) representative: the bottom-right
entry `Gamma0MapUnits (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN) = uвҒ»В№` comes from the
`adjointGamma0Rep_units` identification. -/
private theorem petN_heckeT_p_adjointGamma0Rep_reindex
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k) :
    petN (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN f) g =
      petN (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN
              (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f))
           (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g) := by
  have h := petN_heckeT_p_Gamma1QuotEquiv_reindex p hp hpN
    (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN) f g
  rw [adjointGamma0Rep_units p N hpN] at h
  exact h

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T128 petN-level RHS q-reindex consumer**: analog of
`petN_heckeT_p_adjointGamma0Rep_reindex` for `T_p` on the second slot.
Applying T126 (`slash_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq_diamond_slash_out_inv`) on
slot 1 and T128 (`slash_heckeT_p_cusp_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq`) on slot 2
across the full `вҲ‘_q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё О“вӮҒ(N)` sum, specialized at
`Оі = adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN` (so `Gamma0MapUnits Оі = uвҒ»В№`), yields
`petN f (T_p g) = petN (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ© f) (T_p (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ© g))`.

Together with `petN_heckeT_p_adjointGamma0Rep_reindex`, this is the other half
of the outer two-stage q-reindex used by `petN_heckeT_p_diamond_shift_core`
before any per-q commit. -/
private theorem petN_f_heckeT_p_adjointGamma0Rep_reindex
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k) :
    petN f (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g) =
      petN (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f)
        (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN
          (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g)) := by
  show вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (вҮ‘f вҲЈ[k] (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)
          (вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g) вҲЈ[k] (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) =
      вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f) вҲЈ[k]
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)
          (вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN
              (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g)) вҲЈ[k]
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)
  rw [вҶҗ Equiv.sum_comp (Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
    ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
    (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property)
    (fun q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N =>
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘f вҲЈ[k] (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)
        (вҮ‘(heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g) вҲЈ[k] (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№))]
  refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
  rw [slash_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq_diamond_slash_out_inv
      (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN) f q,
    slash_heckeT_p_cusp_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq p hp hpN
      (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN) g q,
    adjointGamma0Rep_units p N hpN]

/-- **Adjugate `T_p_upper(0) вҶ’ T_p_lower` identity** (GLвӮӮ(в„қ)-level).

Both `peterssonAdj (glMap T_p_upper(0))` and `glMap T_p_lower` have underlying
matrix `[[p, 0], [0, 1]]` over в„қ.  This is the reverse direction of
`peterssonAdj_glMap_T_p_lower_eq_glMap_T_p_upper_zero`; both are needed for
the M_вҲһ-adjoint alignment. -/
private lemma peterssonAdj_glMap_T_p_upper_zero_eq_glMap_T_p_lower
    (p : в„•) (hp : 0 < p) :
    peterssonAdj (glMap (T_p_upper p hp 0) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) =
      (glMap (T_p_lower p hp) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) := by
  apply Units.ext
  ext i j
  have h_L := peterssonAdj_glMap_T_p_upper p hp 0
  simp only [Nat.cast_zero, neg_zero] at h_L
  have h_R : ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
      Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ) = !![(p : в„қ), 0; 0, (1 : в„қ)] := by
    ext i' j'; fin_cases i' <;> fin_cases j' <;> simp [glMap, T_p_lower]
  show (peterssonAdj (glMap (T_p_upper p hp 0) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
      Matrix _ _ в„қ) i j =
    ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) : Matrix _ _ в„қ) i j
  rw [h_L, h_R]

/-- **M_вҲһ adjoint b-collapse alignment helper**: per-summand slash-adjoint
identity aligning the `none` branch of the Option `(Fin p)` family with the
same constant RHS target `(вҮ‘g вҲЈ glMap T_p_upper(0)) вҲЈ mapGL ОівӮҖ` as the
`some b` branch.

Matches the form of `slash_peterssonAdj_T_p_upper_eq_slash_T_p_upper_zero_slash_gamma0`
(the `some b` collapse via `slash_peterssonAdj_T_p_upper_adjointGamma0Rep_inv_eq_T_p_upper_zero`
at any `b вҲҲ Fin p`) but for the `none = M_вҲһ` branch.

**Proof composition.**
* Use `glMap_T_p_upper_inv_mul_M_infty_eq_mapGL_Gamma1` at `b = 0` to derive
  `glMap M_вҲһ = glMap T_p_upper(0) В· mapGL (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)`.
* Take adjoint; use `peterssonAdj_mul` + `peterssonAdj_mapGL_SL_eq_inv` +
  `peterssonAdj_glMap_T_p_upper_zero_eq_glMap_T_p_lower` to simplify
  `peterssonAdj (glMap M_вҲһ)` to
  `mapGL (M_infty_Gamma1_factor 0)вҒ»В№ В· glMap T_p_lower`.
* `M_infty_Gamma1_factor_mem_Gamma1` provides О“вӮҒ(N) membership; its inverse
  is in О“вӮҒ(N), so `вҮ‘g вҲЈ mapGL factorвҒ»В№ = вҮ‘g` by О“вӮҒ(N)-invariance.
* `slash_T_p_lower_eq_T_p_upper_zero_slash_gamma0` converts
  `вҮ‘g вҲЈ glMap T_p_lower` to the common RHS target. -/
private lemma slash_peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq_slash_T_p_upper_zero_slash_gamma0
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k) :
    вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj (glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) =
      (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos 0) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҲЈ[k]
        ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))) := by
  -- Step 1: glMap M_вҲһ = glMap T_p_upper(0) * mapGL (M_infty_Gamma1_factor 0).
  have h_inv_prod :=
    glMap_T_p_upper_inv_mul_M_infty_eq_mapGL_Gamma1 N p hp.pos hpN 0
  have h_M_infty_eq : (glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) =
      (glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos 0) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
        ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) := by
    rw [вҶҗ h_inv_prod, mul_inv_cancel_left]
  -- Step 2: take the adjoint of the factored form.
  rw [h_M_infty_eq, peterssonAdj_mul, peterssonAdj_mapGL_SL_eq_inv,
    peterssonAdj_glMap_T_p_upper_zero_eq_glMap_T_p_lower]
  -- Step 3: rewrite `(mapGL в„қ factor)вҒ»В№` as `mapGL в„қ factorвҒ»В№`.
  rw [вҶҗ map_inv, SlashAction.slash_mul]
  -- Step 4: `factorвҒ»В№ вҲҲ О“вӮҒ(N)` acts trivially on `g`.
  have hfactor_mem := M_infty_Gamma1_factor_mem_Gamma1 N p hpN 0
  have hfactor_inv_mem : (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)вҒ»В№ вҲҲ Gamma1 N :=
    inv_mem hfactor_mem
  have h_g_slash : вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
        (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)вҒ»В№) = вҮ‘g :=
    SlashInvariantFormClass.slash_action_eq g _
      вҹЁ(M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)вҒ»В№, hfactor_inv_mem, rflвҹ©
  rw [h_g_slash]
  -- Step 5: T_p_lower вҶ’ T_p_upper(0) + ОівӮҖ bridge.
  exact slash_T_p_lower_eq_T_p_upper_zero_slash_gamma0 p hp hpN g

/-- **T024 uniform peterssonAdj M_вҲһ slash on cusp form**: for cusp form `g`,
`g вҲЈ peterssonAdj M_вҲһ = g вҲЈ T_p_lower`. Combines
`slash_peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq_slash_T_p_upper_zero_slash_gamma0`
(which gives `(g вҲЈ T_p_upper(0)) вҲЈ ОівӮҖ`) with
`slash_T_p_lower_eq_T_p_upper_zero_slash_gamma0.symm` (which converts back to
`g вҲЈ T_p_lower`).

This is the **M_вҲһ branch** of the uniform `g вҲЈ peterssonAdj Оұ = g вҲЈ T_p_lower`
identity for `Оұ вҲҲ T_p reps`, key to the petN T_p-side reduction
`petN(T_p f, g) = peterssonInner k (T_p В· О“вӮҒ_FD) f (g вҲЈ T_p_lower)`. -/
private lemma slash_peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq_slash_T_p_lower
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k) :
    вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj (glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) =
      вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] (glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) := by
  rw [slash_peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq_slash_T_p_upper_zero_slash_gamma0
    p hp hpN g]
  exact (slash_T_p_lower_eq_T_p_upper_zero_slash_gamma0 p hp hpN g).symm

/-- **T024 uniform peterssonAdj T_p_upper(b) slash on cusp form**: for cusp
form `g` and any `b : в„•`, `g вҲЈ peterssonAdj T_p_upper(b) = g вҲЈ T_p_lower`.
Composes:
* `peterssonAdj_T_p_upper_eq_shift_mul_lower`: `peterssonAdj T_p_upper(b)
  = mapGL (shiftSL_loc(-b)) В· glMap T_p_lower`;
* `SlashAction.slash_mul`: distributes the slash;
* `SlashInvariantFormClass.slash_action_eq` with
  `shiftSL_loc_mem_Gamma1`: `g вҲЈ shiftSL_loc(-b) = g`.

This is the **T_p_upper(b) branch** of the uniform
`g вҲЈ peterssonAdj Оұ = g вҲЈ T_p_lower` identity for `Оұ вҲҲ T_p reps`. -/
private lemma slash_peterssonAdj_glMap_T_p_upper_eq_slash_T_p_lower
    (p : в„•) (hp : 0 < p) (b : в„•)
    (g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k) :
    вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj (glMap (T_p_upper p hp b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) =
      вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] (glMap (T_p_lower p hp) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) := by
  rw [peterssonAdj_T_p_upper_eq_shift_mul_lower p hp b, SlashAction.slash_mul,
    show (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
      (shiftSL_loc (-(b : в„Ө))) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) = вҮ‘g from
        SlashInvariantFormClass.slash_action_eq g _
          вҹЁshiftSL_loc (-(b : в„Ө)), shiftSL_loc_mem_Gamma1 _, rflвҹ©]

/-! ### T128 DS-standard `Оҙ_b` representative-system helpers

The `Оҙ_b вҲҲ О“вӮҒ(N)` matrix realizing `ОівӮҖ В· T_p_upper(b) = T_p_lower В· Оҙ_b` for
`ОівӮҖ = adjointGamma0Rep`.  These are the candidates for a complete
representative system of `H_L \ О“вӮҒ(N)` where
`H_L := О“вӮҒ(N) вҲ© T_p_lowerвҒ»В№ В· О“вӮҒ(N) В· T_p_lower`. -/

/-- **T128 lower-branch `Оҙ_b` О“вӮҒ(N)-factor.**  The SL(2, в„Ө) matrix
`!![1, b вҲ’ gcdB(p,N); N, Nb + p В· gcdA(p,N)]`.  Realizes
`ОівӮҖ В· T_p_upper(b) = T_p_lower В· mapGL Оҙ_b` as GL(2, в„қ) elements, where
`ОівӮҖ = adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN`. -/
private noncomputable def gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor
    (N p : в„•) [NeZero N] (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N) (b : в„•) : SL(2, в„Ө) :=
  вҹЁ!![1, (b : в„Ө) - Int.gcdB p N;
      (N : в„Ө), (N : в„Ө) * b + (p : в„Ө) * Int.gcdA p N],
    by
      have hbez := Int.gcd_eq_gcd_ab (p : в„Ө) (N : в„Ө)
      rw [show (Int.gcd (вҶ‘p) (вҶ‘N) : в„Ө) = 1 from by exact_mod_cast hpN] at hbez
      rw [Matrix.det_fin_two_of]; linarithвҹ©

/-- **T128: `gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor` lies in `О“вӮҒ(N)`.** -/
private theorem gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor_mem_Gamma1
    (N p : в„•) [NeZero N] (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N) (b : в„•) :
    gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b вҲҲ Gamma1 N := by
  rw [Gamma1_mem]
  have hbez := Int.gcd_eq_gcd_ab (p : в„Ө) (N : в„Ө)
  rw [show (Int.gcd (вҶ‘p) (вҶ‘N) : в„Ө) = 1 from by exact_mod_cast hpN] at hbez
  have hN_zmod : ((N : в„•) : ZMod N) = 0 := ZMod.natCast_self N
  have hpgcdA_mod : ((p : ZMod N) : ZMod N) * ((Int.gcdA p N : в„Ө) : ZMod N) = 1 := by
    have := congr_arg ((вҶ‘) : в„Ө вҶ’ ZMod N) hbez.symm
    push_cast at this
    -- `this` is вҶ‘p * вҶ‘(gcdA p N) + вҶ‘N * вҶ‘(gcdB p N) = 1 in ZMod N
    rw [hN_zmod, zero_mul, add_zero] at this
    exact this
  refine вҹЁ?_, ?_, ?_вҹ©
  В· change ((1 : в„Ө) : ZMod N) = 1
    push_cast; rfl
  В· change (((N : в„Ө) * b + (p : в„Ө) * Int.gcdA p N : в„Ө) : ZMod N) = 1
    push_cast
    rw [hN_zmod]
    simp only [zero_mul, zero_add]
    exact hpgcdA_mod
  В· change (((N : в„Ө) : в„Ө) : ZMod N) = 0
    push_cast
    exact ZMod.natCast_self N

/-- **T128: The DS-standard matrix identity**: for `ОівӮҖ = adjointGamma0Rep
p N hpN` and any `b : в„•`, `ОівӮҖ В· T_p_upper(b) = T_p_lower В· mapGL Оҙ_b`
in `GL(2, в„қ)`, where `Оҙ_b = gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b`. -/
private theorem mapGL_gamma0_mul_T_p_upper_eq_T_p_lower_mul_mapGL_delta
    (N p : в„•) [NeZero N] (hp : 0 < p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N) (b : в„•) :
    ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _)
        ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
      (glMap (T_p_upper p hp b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) =
    (glMap (T_p_lower p hp) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
      ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _)
        (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) := by
  -- Direct matrix comparison.
  apply Units.ext
  ext i j
  have hbez : (Int.gcdA p N : в„Ө) * p + (Int.gcdB p N : в„Ө) * N = 1 := by
    have h := Int.gcd_eq_gcd_ab (p : в„Ө) (N : в„Ө)
    rw [show (Int.gcd (вҶ‘p) (вҶ‘N) : в„Ө) = 1 from by exact_mod_cast hpN] at h
    linarith
  -- Unfold ОівӮҖ = adjointGamma0Rep = !![p, -gcdB; N, gcdA] (over в„қ).
  have h_gamma0_mat : (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _)
      ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
      Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ) =
      !![(p : в„қ), -((Int.gcdB p N : в„Ө) : в„қ); (N : в„қ), ((Int.gcdA p N : в„Ө) : в„қ)] := by
    ext i' j'
    fin_cases i' <;> fin_cases j' <;>
      simp [adjointGamma0Rep, mapGL_coe_matrix, algebraMap_int_eq, Matrix.of_apply]
  have h_Tu_mat : ((glMap (T_p_upper p hp b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
      Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ) = !![(1 : в„қ), (b : в„қ); 0, (p : в„қ)] := by
    ext i' j'; fin_cases i' <;> fin_cases j' <;>
      simp [glMap, T_p_upper, Matrix.GeneralLinearGroup.mkOfDetNeZero,
        Matrix.GeneralLinearGroup.map, Matrix.of_apply]
  have h_Tl_mat : ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
      Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ) = !![(p : в„қ), 0; 0, 1] := by
    ext i' j'; fin_cases i' <;> fin_cases j' <;>
      simp [glMap, T_p_lower, Matrix.GeneralLinearGroup.mkOfDetNeZero,
        Matrix.GeneralLinearGroup.map, Matrix.of_apply]
  have h_delta_mat : (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _)
      (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) :
      Matrix (Fin 2) (Fin 2) в„қ) =
      !![(1 : в„қ), ((b : в„қ) - ((Int.gcdB p N : в„Ө) : в„қ));
         (N : в„қ), ((N : в„қ) * b + (p : в„қ) * ((Int.gcdA p N : в„Ө) : в„қ))] := by
    ext i' j'; fin_cases i' <;> fin_cases j' <;>
      simp [mapGL_coe_matrix, gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor, algebraMap_int_eq,
        Matrix.of_apply]
  show ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _)
        ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө)) *
      (glMap (T_p_upper p hp b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ).val i j =
    ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
      ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _)
        (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)).val i j
  rw [Units.val_mul, Units.val_mul, h_gamma0_mat, h_Tu_mat, h_Tl_mat, h_delta_mat]
  fin_cases i <;> fin_cases j <;>
    simp [Matrix.mul_apply, Fin.sum_univ_two, Matrix.of_apply] <;> ring

/-- **T128 `M_вҲһ` branch of the DS p+1 coset family factorization**:
the `M_вҲһ` analog of `mapGL_gamma0_mul_T_p_upper_eq_T_p_lower_mul_mapGL_delta`.

`ОівӮҖ В· M_вҲһ = T_p_lower В· mapGL Оө` where
`Оө := gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 * M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0`
is a product of two О“вӮҒ(N) elements (hence in О“вӮҒ(N)).

Together with the upper-family factorization, this establishes the algebraic
p+1 coset-family identification `ОівӮҖ В· Оұ_i = T_p_lower В· ОҙМғ_i` for every
`i : Option (Fin p)`, where `Оұ_some_b = glMap (T_p_upper p hp b)`,
`Оұ_none = glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN)`, and `ОҙМғ_i вҲҲ О“вӮҒ(N)`.  This is the
double-coset bijection underlying DS Theorem 5.5.3.

**Proof**: chain
* `glMap M_вҲһ = glMap T_p_upper(0) В· mapGL (M_infty_Gamma1_factor 0)` (from
  `glMap_T_p_upper_inv_mul_M_infty_eq_mapGL_Gamma1`, via `mul_inv_cancel_left`),
* `ОівӮҖ В· T_p_upper(0) = T_p_lower В· Оҙ_0` (via the upper-family factorization
  `mapGL_gamma0_mul_T_p_upper_eq_T_p_lower_mul_mapGL_delta` at `b = 0`),
* multiplicativity of `mapGL в„қ` to collect the two О“вӮҒ(N) factors. -/
private theorem mapGL_gamma0_mul_M_infty_eq_T_p_lower_mul_mapGL_epsilon
    (N p : в„•) [NeZero N] (hp : 0 < p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N) :
    ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _)
        ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
      (glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) =
    (glMap (T_p_lower p hp) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
      ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _)
        (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 *
          M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) := by
  have h_M_infty_eq : (glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) =
      (glMap (T_p_upper p hp 0) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
        ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) (M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) := by
    rw [вҶҗ glMap_T_p_upper_inv_mul_M_infty_eq_mapGL_Gamma1 N p hp hpN 0,
      mul_inv_cancel_left]
  rw [h_M_infty_eq, вҶҗ mul_assoc,
    mapGL_gamma0_mul_T_p_upper_eq_T_p_lower_mul_mapGL_delta N p hp hpN 0,
    mul_assoc, вҶҗ map_mul]

/-- **T128 `M_вҲһ` branch О“вӮҒ(N)-membership**: the correction factor `Оө` from
`mapGL_gamma0_mul_M_infty_eq_T_p_lower_mul_mapGL_epsilon` lies in О“вӮҒ(N), as a
product of two О“вӮҒ(N) elements (the Оҙ_0 factor + the M_вҲһ factor at b = 0). -/
private theorem gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor_zero_mul_M_infty_Gamma1_factor_zero_mem_Gamma1
    (N p : в„•) [NeZero N] (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N) :
    gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 * M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 вҲҲ
      Gamma1 N :=
  mul_mem (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor_mem_Gamma1 N p hpN 0)
    (M_infty_Gamma1_factor_mem_Gamma1 N p hpN 0)

/-- **T128 p+1 coset family О“вӮҒ(N)-correction**: the Option (Fin p)-indexed
family of О“вӮҒ(N) correction factors `ОҙМғ_i` satisfying
`ОівӮҖ В· Оұ_i = T_p_lower В· mapGL (ОҙМғ_i)`, where
`Оұ_some_b = glMap (T_p_upper p hp b)`, `Оұ_none = glMap (M_infty N p hp hpN)`.

This packages the p+1 DS coset-family identification into a single
`Option (Fin p)`-indexed family, giving the algebraic backbone of the
sum-level double-coset aggregation. -/
private noncomputable def ds_p_plus_one_family_Gamma1_factor
    (N p : в„•) [NeZero N] (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N) :
    Option (Fin p) вҶ’ SL(2, в„Ө)
  | none => gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 * M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0
  | some b => gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN b.val

/-- **T128 p+1 coset family О“вӮҒ(N)-membership**: every member of the
correction family `ds_p_plus_one_family_Gamma1_factor` lies in О“вӮҒ(N). -/
private theorem ds_p_plus_one_family_Gamma1_factor_mem_Gamma1
    (N p : в„•) [NeZero N] (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N) (i : Option (Fin p)) :
    ds_p_plus_one_family_Gamma1_factor N p hpN i вҲҲ Gamma1 N := by
  match i with
  | none =>
    exact gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor_zero_mul_M_infty_Gamma1_factor_zero_mem_Gamma1
      N p hpN
  | some b =>
    exact gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor_mem_Gamma1 N p hpN b.val

/-- **T128 p+1 coset family aggregate factorization**: uniform statement of
