                GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (ModularGroup.fd : Set в„Қ))
            вҮ‘f (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] (glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) := fun q =>
