open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T024 sum-level joint absorption consumer**: applies the per-q
M_вҲһ/upper-b joint absorption helpers
(`per_q_M_infty_branch_full_absorb`, `per_q_T_p_upper_branch_full_absorb`)
across the Пғ-reindexed RHS distributed sum.  Specifically, takes the
output of `petN_diamond_heckeT_p_symm_RHS_sum_distributed_reindex` (the
Пғ-reindexed RHS distributed sum) and rewrites each per-q summand using
the per-q joint absorption helpers, transforming each branch's slot-1
Пғ-shifted f-slash into a plain `q.outвҒ»В№` slash (with `f` un-diamond-shifted)
and slot-2's `(M_вҲһ or T_p_upper b) * (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№` slash on `g` into the
`T_p_lower * Оі_X * (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№` form (with `g` diamond-shifted to `вҹЁuвҹ© g`).

