            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))) p

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T024 DS adjoint standard form via closed branches.**

End-of-chain SMO-critical consumer: composes
`peterssonInner_per_q_distributed_form_via_closed_branches` (per-`q` closed-
branch identity) with `petN_diamond_heckeT_p_symm_RHS_sum_distributed`
(`petN(вҹЁpвҹ© f, T_p g) = вҲ‘_q [per-q distributed RHS]`) and the existing standard-
form-of-LHS-bridge consumer to produce the DS 5.5.3 standard form
`petN(T_p f, g) = petN(f, вҹЁpвҹ©вҒ»В№ T_p g)`.

Inputs (the irreducible atomic content of DS 5.5.2(b)):

* `tile : вҲҖ q, Fin (p + 1) вҶ’ Set в„Қ` вҖ” the q-indexed tile family; the closed
  branches require all `p + 1` tiles to AE-equal `(ОівӮҖвҒ»В№ * q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd`
  (geometric content of the bundle's coset construction).
* `h_tile_eq` вҖ” per-q, per-tile shape AE-equality.
* `h_LHS_eq_closed_branch_sum` вҖ” the **LHS connection bridge**:
  `petN(T_p f, g)` equals the sum over `q` of the closed-branch LHS form
  (M_вҲһ branch + ОЈ_b T_p_upper(b) branch with q-independent g_const but
  q-dependent tile shapes). This is the analytic content connecting petN to
  the bundle structure (typically discharged via the Q-reindex
  `petN_heckeT_p_adjointGamma0Rep_reindex` + per-q distribute machinery).

**Mathematical reference.**  DiamondвҖ“Shurman, *A First Course in Modular
Forms*, Prop. 5.5.2(b) and Thm. 5.5.3; Miyake В§4.5. -/
private theorem petN_heckeT_p_adjoint_standard_form_via_closed_branches
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k)
    (tile : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N вҶ’ Fin (p + 1) вҶ’ Set UpperHalfPlane)
    (h_tile_eq : вҲҖ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N, вҲҖ i : Fin (p + 1),
      tile q i =бөҗ[Ој_hyp]
      (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) :
          GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
        ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№)) вҖў ModularGroup.fd)
    (h_LHS_eq_closed_branch_sum :
      petN (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN f) g =
      вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        (peterssonInner k (tile q 0) вҮ‘f
            (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
              ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
                ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө)) :
                  GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) +
          вҲ‘ b : Fin p, peterssonInner k (tile q b.succ) вҮ‘f
            (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
              ((glMap (T_p_upper p hp.pos b.val) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
                ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө)) :
                  GL (Fin 2) в„қ))))) :
    petN (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN f) g =
      petN f (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№
        (heckeT_p_cusp k p hp hpN g)) := by
  refine petN_heckeT_p_adjoint_standard_form_of_LHS_bridge p hp hpN f g ?_
  rw [h_LHS_eq_closed_branch_sum,
    petN_diamond_heckeT_p_symm_RHS_sum_distributed p hp hpN f g]
  refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
  exact peterssonInner_per_q_distributed_form_via_closed_branches p hp hpN q g вҮ‘f
    (tile q) (h_tile_eq q)

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T024 LHS bridge from per-q to global closed-branch sum.**

Aggregator: lifts per-`q` LHS connection identifications to the **global**
`h_LHS_eq_closed_branch_sum` hypothesis required by
`petN_heckeT_p_adjoint_standard_form_via_closed_branches`.

The per-`q` connection equates the petN-summand at `q` (i.e.,
`peterssonInner k fd (вҮ‘(T_p f) вҲЈ[k] q.outвҒ»В№) (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] q.outвҒ»В№)`) to the
