/-- **T024 per-q LHS connection theorem.**

Supplies `h_per_q_LHS_eq_closed_branch_sum` (the per-q hypothesis required by
`petN_LHS_eq_closed_branch_sum_via_per_q`) from the existing per-q DS p+1 family
