open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T024 sum-level slash-adjoint coset reduction for M_вҲһ slot-swap.**

Per-`q` application of `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset` over the
quotient sum: for each `q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N`, swaps the slash on
slot-1 (carrying `glMap M_вҲһ`) with `peterssonAdj` action on slot-2,
shifting `fd` by `M_вҲһ вҖў q.outвҒ»В№`.

First sum-level reduction step of the M_вҲһ slot-swap infrastructure used
to discharge `h_M_infty_tile_shift_to_prefactored`. -/
private theorem M_infty_slot_swap_LHS_via_slash_adjoint_coset
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (F G : UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) :
    (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (F вҲЈ[k] ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
          (G вҲЈ[k] ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
    вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k
        ((glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў
          (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў
            (ModularGroup.fd : Set UpperHalfPlane)))
        F
        (G вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj (glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) := by
  refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
  exact peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset
    (glMap (M_infty N p hp.pos hpN))
    (glMap_M_infty_det_pos N p hp.pos hpN) (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө)) F G

