open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T090 reduction of `h_M_infty_tile_shift_to_prefactored` to the
fundamental-domain slash-exchange residual.**

Composes the existing three sum-level transformations on the LHS:

1. `peterssonInner_sum_M_infty_residual_LHS_to_dist`: residual M_вҲһ-shifted-tile
   LHS вҶ’ fd-distributed LHS (per-q `peterssonInner_slash_adj_M_infty_q_summand_eq.symm`,
   converting `(M_вҲһ вҖў q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd` domain to `fd` with `вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©f вҲЈ M_вҲһ В· q.outвҒ»В№`
   on slot-1 and `вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©g вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№` on slot-2).
2. `peterssonInner_sum_M_infty_LHS_dist_slot2_to_sigma`: per-q slot-2 Пғ-shift
   absorption (`slash_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq_diamond_slash_out_inv_GL.symm`),
   converting `вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©g вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№` to `g вҲЈ (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№` where
   `Пғ = Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN)`.
3. `peterssonInner_sum_M_infty_LHS_dist_slot1_unfactor_diamond`: per-q slot-1
   diamond-M_вҲһ unfactor (`slash_diamond_inv_M_infty_eq_T_p_lower_epsilon`),
   converting `вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©f вҲЈ M_вҲһ В· q.outвҒ»В№` to
   `f вҲЈ T_p_lower В· Оі_XВ·Оі_Y В· q.outвҒ»В№`.

After these three, the LHS is in the canonical "post-normalization" form, with
neither `вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©` shifts nor shifted-tile domains visible вҖ” only explicit slash
chains visible as `T_p_lower В· Оі_XВ·Оі_Y В· q.outвҒ»В№` on slot-1 and
`(Пғ q).outвҒ»В№` on slot-2.

**The remaining hypothesis** `h_FD_slash_exchange` is then a precise sum-level
slash-adjoint exchange at the О“вӮҒ(N)-fundamental-domain level:
`f вҲЈ T_p_lower В· Оі_XВ·Оі_Y В· q.outвҒ»В№` (with slot-1 `T_p_lower`-correction shape)
exchanges with `g вҲЈ M_вҲһ В· (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№` (with slot-2 `M_вҲһ`-correction shape) under
the Пғ-reindex of `q`. This is the **single irreducible blocker** for the
M_вҲһ branch of `petN_heckeT_p_adjoint_standard_form`'s residual: no shifted-tile
domain, no diamond shifts, just a sum-level FD-integral matching identity.

**Use site.** Discharging `h_FD_slash_exchange` directly closes
`h_M_infty_tile_shift_to_prefactored`, which (combined with the upper-b
analog) closes `petN_heckeT_p_adjoint_standard_form` via
`petN_heckeT_p_adjoint_standard_form_from_two_tile_shift_residuals`. -/
private theorem h_M_infty_tile_shift_to_prefactored_of_FD_slash_exchange
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k)
    (h_FD_slash_exchange :
      (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
            (вҮ‘f вҲЈ[k]
              ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
                ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                  (gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0 *
                    M_infty_Gamma1_factor N p hpN 0)) *
                ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                  (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
            (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
              ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
                  (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
