open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T090 per-(Оұ, Оі_Оұ) general slash factorization (per-q).**

Generalizes both `slash_diamond_inv_M_infty_eq_T_p_lower_epsilon` (for Оұ = M_вҲһ,
Оі_Оұ = Оі_XВ·Оі_Y) and `slash_diamond_inv_T_p_upper_eq_T_p_lower_delta` (for
Оұ = T_p_upper(b), Оі_Оұ = Оі_b) under a single matrix-factorization hypothesis.

Given the per-Оұ matrix identity `ОівӮҖ В· Оұ = T_p_lower В· mapGL Оі_Оұ` in `GL(2, в„қ)`
(satisfied by both DS Prop. 5.5.2(b) families per the existing
`mapGL_gamma0_mul_M_infty_eq_T_p_lower_mul_mapGL_epsilon` /
`mapGL_gamma0_mul_T_p_upper_eq_T_p_lower_mul_mapGL_delta`), the per-q slash
identity holds:

```
вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©g вҲЈ[k] (Оұ В· mapGL qвҒ»В№) = g вҲЈ[k] (T_p_lower В· mapGL Оі_Оұ В· mapGL qвҒ»В№)
```

This is the per-q "matrix factorization step" used by both the M_вҲһ and upper-b
chain Step 3 (slot-1 diamond unfactor). -/
private lemma slash_diamond_inv_Оұ_eq_T_p_lower_via_matrix_factor
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) (Оі_Оұ : SL(2, в„Ө))
    (h_factor : ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _)
        ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) * Оұ =
        (glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) Оі_Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
    (q : SL(2, в„Ө)) (g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k) :
    (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g) вҲЈ[k]
      (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
    вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
      ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
        ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ) Оі_Оұ) *
        ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ) qвҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) := by
  have h_diamond : (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g) :
      UpperHalfPlane вҶ’ в„Ӯ) =
      вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
        ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))) := by
    show вҮ‘(diamondOpCusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g) = _
    rw [diamondOpCusp_eq k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№
      (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN) (adjointGamma0Rep_units p N hpN)]
    rfl
  rw [h_diamond, вҶҗ SlashAction.slash_mul, вҶҗ mul_assoc, h_factor]

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T090 per-Оұ common FD slash-exchange reduction.**

Unifies the M_вҲһ and upper-b FD slash-exchange residuals under a single
per-Оұ reduction theorem. Given the per-Оұ matrix factorization
`ОівӮҖ В· Оұ = T_p_lower В· mapGL Оі_Оұ` (with Оі_Оұ : SL(2, в„Ө)), the FD slash-exchange
residual in `T_p_lower В· Оі_Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№` form is logically equivalent (via a
per-q `Finset.sum_congr` consumer of
`slash_diamond_inv_Оұ_eq_T_p_lower_via_matrix_factor.symm`) to the canonical
`Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№` form:

```
вҲ‘_q peterssonInner k fd (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©f вҲЈ Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№) (g вҲЈ (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№)
  = вҲ‘_q peterssonInner k fd (f вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№) (g вҲЈ Оұ В· (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№)
```

For both branches, the matrix factorization is provided by existing lemmas:
* M_вҲһ branch: `mapGL_gamma0_mul_M_infty_eq_T_p_lower_mul_mapGL_epsilon`,
  with Оұ = `glMap M_вҲһ`, Оі_Оұ = `gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor 0 *
  M_infty_Gamma1_factor 0`.
* upper-b branch (per b): `mapGL_gamma0_mul_T_p_upper_eq_T_p_lower_mul_mapGL_delta`,
  with Оұ = `glMap T_p_upper(b)`, Оі_Оұ = `gamma0_T_p_upper_Gamma1_factor b`.

**Role.** Common reduction lemma: discharging the **same canonical-form
hypothesis at every Оұ** (M_вҲһ and T_p_upper(b) for b вҲҲ range p) suffices to
close all FD slash-exchange residuals via this single reduction. -/
private theorem h_Оұ_FD_slash_exchange_T_p_lower_form_of_canonical
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) (Оі_Оұ : SL(2, в„Ө))
    (h_factor : ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _)
        ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө)) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) * Оұ =
        (glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* _) Оі_Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k)
    (h_canonical_Оұ :
      (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
            (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f) вҲЈ[k]
              (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
            (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
              ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
                  (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                  SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
      вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
            (вҮ‘f вҲЈ[k] ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№))
            (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
              (Оұ *
                ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                  ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                    ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
                    (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                    SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))) :
    (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (вҮ‘f вҲЈ[k]
            ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
              ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ) Оі_Оұ) *
              ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
          (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
                (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
    вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (вҮ‘f вҲЈ[k] ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№))
          (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
            (Оұ *
              ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                  ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
                  (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                  SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) := by
  -- Per-q apply matrix factorization (`slash_diamond_inv_Оұ_eq_T_p_lower_via_matrix_factor.symm`)
  -- to LHS slot 1, converting `f вҲЈ T_p_lowerВ·Оі_ОұВ·q.outвҒ»В№` to `вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©f вҲЈ ОұВ·q.outвҒ»В№`.
  rw [show (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘f вҲЈ[k]
          ((glMap (T_p_lower p hp.pos) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) *
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ) Оі_Оұ) *
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
        (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
              ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
              (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
              SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
    вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f) вҲЈ[k]
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
        (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
              ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
              (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
              SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
    from Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => by
      congr 1
      exact (slash_diamond_inv_Оұ_eq_T_p_lower_via_matrix_factor p hp hpN Оұ Оі_Оұ
        h_factor (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө)) f).symm]
  exact h_canonical_Оұ

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T090 per-Оұ canonical-from-balanced reduction (Пғ-absorption).**

Reduces the per-Оұ canonical sum-level Пғ-absorption identity to the
**balanced** form (with no `Пғ q` on either side, only `q.outвҒ»В№`):

```
вҲ‘_q peterssonInner k fd (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©f вҲЈ Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№) (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©g вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№)
  = вҲ‘_q peterssonInner k fd (вҹЁuвҹ©f вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№) (g вҲЈ Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№)
```

This is the **structurally simplest form** of the per-Оұ slash-exchange
content: no Пғ-permutation, no shifted-tile domains, just FD-level
slash chains with explicit diamond shifts on either f or g.

**Proof.** Composes two existing per-q rewrites:
* LHS canonical вҶ’ LHS balanced via slot-2 Пғ-correction
  (`slash_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq_diamond_slash_out_inv_GL` applied to g).
* RHS balanced вҶ’ RHS canonical via `Equiv.sum_comp` over Пғ + slot-1
  Пғ-correction on `вҹЁuвҹ©f` (giving `вҹЁuвҹ©f вҲЈ (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№ = вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©(вҹЁuвҹ©f) вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№ = f вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№`).

**Role.** Generic per-Оұ reduction: discharging the **same balanced identity
at every Оұ** (M_вҲһ and T_p_upper(b) for b вҲҲ range p) suffices to close all
canonical FD slash-exchange identities (and hence, via the existing
matrix-factorization reduction `h_Оұ_FD_slash_exchange_T_p_lower_form_of_canonical`,
the per-Оұ tile-shift residual).

**Combined with the matrix-factorization reduction**, both M_вҲһ and upper-b
FD slash-exchange residuals reduce to ONE explicit balanced sum-level identity
per Оұ вҖ” the maximally simplified form of the genuine analytic content. -/
private theorem h_Оұ_canonical_form_of_balanced
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k)
    (h_balanced :
      (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
            (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f) вҲЈ[k]
              (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
            (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g) вҲЈ[k]
              ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
      вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
            (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) вҲЈ[k]
              ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
            (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
              (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
                (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))) :
    (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f) вҲЈ[k]
            (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
          (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
                (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
    вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (вҮ‘f вҲЈ[k] ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№))
          (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
            (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
                ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
                (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
                SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) := by
  -- Step A: LHS canonical вҶ’ LHS balanced via per-q slot-2 Пғ-correction.
  have h_LHS : (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f) вҲЈ[k]
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
        (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
              ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
              (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
              SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
    вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f) вҲЈ[k]
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g) вҲЈ[k]
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) := by
    refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
    congr 1
    have h := slash_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq_diamond_slash_out_inv_GL
      (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN) g q
    rw [adjointGamma0Rep_units p N hpN] at h
    exact h
  -- Step B: RHS balanced вҶ’ RHS canonical via Equiv.sum_comp Пғ + per-q slot-1
  -- Пғ-correction on вҹЁuвҹ©f (using вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©(вҹЁuвҹ©f) = f).
  have h_RHS : (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) вҲЈ[k]
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
        (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))) =
    вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘f вҲЈ[k] ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№))
        (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            ((Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
              ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
              (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property q).out :
              SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) := by
    -- Set Пғ = Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0 (adjointGamma0Rep) and apply Пғ.sum_comp
    -- to LHS of h_RHS (= balanced_RHS).
    -- Пғ.sum_comp F : ОЈ_q F(Пғ q) = ОЈ_q F(q). So balanced_RHS = ОЈ_q F(Пғ q) where
    -- F(q) = peterssonInner k fd (вҹЁuвҹ©f вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№) (g вҲЈ Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№).
    -- Then per-q, F(Пғ q) = peterssonInner k fd (вҹЁuвҹ©f вҲЈ (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№)
    --                                        (g вҲЈ Оұ В· (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№)
    -- and the slot-1 Пғ-correction `вҹЁuвҹ©f вҲЈ (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№ = f вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№` matches
    -- canonical_RHS_q.
    set Пғ : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N вүғ SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N :=
      Gamma1QuotEquivOfGamma0
        ((adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN : Gamma0 N) : SL(2, в„Ө))
        (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN).property
    rw [вҶҗ Пғ.sum_comp (fun q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N =>
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) вҲЈ[k]
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
        (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))))]
    -- Goal: вҲ‘_q F(Пғ q) = canonical_RHS where
    -- F(Пғ q) = peterssonInner k fd (вҹЁuвҹ©f вҲЈ (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№) (g вҲЈ Оұ В· (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№)
    refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
    -- Per-q goal: F(Пғ q) = canonical_RHS_q.
    -- Slot 2 matches: g вҲЈ Оұ В· (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№.
    -- Slot 1: вҹЁuвҹ©f вҲЈ (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№ = f вҲЈ q.outвҒ»В№.
    congr 1
    have h := slash_Gamma1QuotEquiv_out_inv_eq_diamond_slash_out_inv_GL
      (adjointGamma0Rep p N hpN)
      (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) q
    rw [adjointGamma0Rep_units p N hpN] at h
    -- h : вҮ‘(вҹЁuвҹ©f) вҲЈ mapGL (Пғ q).outвҒ»В№ = вҮ‘(вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©(вҹЁuвҹ©f)) вҲЈ mapGL q.outвҒ»В№
    rw [h]
    -- Goal: вҮ‘(вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©(вҹЁuвҹ©f)) вҲЈ mapGL q.outвҒ»В№ = вҮ‘f вҲЈ mapGL q.outвҒ»В№
    congr 1
    -- Goal: вҮ‘(вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©(вҹЁuвҹ©f)) = вҮ‘f
    show вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№
      (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) = вҮ‘f
    have h_cancel : diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№
        (diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) = f := by
      show diamondOpCusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№
        (diamondOpCusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) = f
      rw [show diamondOpCusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№
          (diamondOpCusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) =
          ((diamondOpCusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№).comp
            (diamondOpCusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN))) f from rfl,
        вҶҗ diamondOpCusp_mul, inv_mul_cancel, diamondOpCusp_one]
      rfl
    rw [h_cancel]
  -- Combine: canonical_LHS = balanced_LHS = balanced_RHS = canonical_RHS.
  rw [h_LHS, h_balanced, h_RHS]

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T090 per-Оұ aggregate-FD-balance reduction.**

Reduces the per-Оұ balanced sum identity (the irreducible content of both M_вҲһ
and upper-b FD slash-exchange residuals) to a single Petersson integral
balance at the **union of Оұ-shifted О“вӮҒ(N) tiles**:

```
peterssonInner k (вӢғ_q (Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd) (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©f) (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©g вҲЈ peterssonAdj Оұ)
  = peterssonInner k (вӢғ_q (Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd) (вҹЁuвҹ©f вҲЈ peterssonAdj Оұ) g
```

**Composition.** Applies `peterssonInner_sum_slash_adjoint_coset_aggregate`
(LHS, slash-on-slot-1) and `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset_right` +
`peterssonInner_iUnion_finite_aedisjoint` (RHS, slash-on-slot-2)
symmetrically, then uses the FD-balance hypothesis to equate the resulting
single Petersson integrals over the same union domain.

**Hypotheses.** Standard tile-family hypotheses for the Оұ-shifted tiles
`{(Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd : q вҲҲ SL(2,в„Ө) в§ё О“вӮҒ(N)}`:
* `hОұ`: positivity of `Оұ.det.val`;
* `hd`: pairwise AE-disjointness;
* `hm`: NullMeasurableSet of each tile;
* `hint_LHS`/`hint_RHS`: integrability of the LHS/RHS petersson integrands
  on the union (with `peterssonAdj Оұ` applied).

**For both DS Prop. 5.5.2(b) families** (M_вҲһ and T_p_upper(b)), the
positivity is provided by `glMap_M_infty_det_pos` /
`glMap_T_p_upper_det_pos`, AE-disjointness/measurability/integrability are
provided by existing helpers.

**Single irreducible blocker.** The remaining hypothesis `h_FD_balance` is
the genuine analytic content: a Petersson integral identity at the level
of the Оұ-shifted О“вӮҒ(N) tile union. Closing this for `Оұ вҲҲ {glMap M_вҲһ} вҲӘ
{glMap T_p_upper(b) : b вҲҲ range p}` discharges all FD slash-exchange
residuals via composition with the prior T090 reductions
(`h_Оұ_canonical_form_of_balanced`,
`h_Оұ_FD_slash_exchange_T_p_lower_form_of_canonical`,
`h_Оұ_tile_shift_to_prefactored_of_FD_slash_exchange` /
`h_upper_tile_shift_to_prefactored_of_FD_slash_exchange`,
`petN_heckeT_p_adjoint_standard_form_from_two_FD_slash_exchanges`,
`petN_heckeT_p_diamond_shift_core_of_unsymm`). -/
private theorem balanced_Оұ_of_aggregate_FD_balance
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) (hОұ : 0 < Оұ.det.val)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k)
    (hd : Pairwise (fun (qвӮҒ qвӮӮ : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N) =>
      AEDisjoint Ој_hyp
        ((Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (qвӮҒ.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
        ((Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (qвӮӮ.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў fd)))
    (hm : вҲҖ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      NullMeasurableSet
        ((Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ)) Ој_hyp)
    (hint_LHS : IntegrableOn
      (fun П„ => petersson k
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f))
        ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g)) вҲЈ[k]
          peterssonAdj Оұ) П„)
      (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ)) Ој_hyp)
    (hint_RHS : IntegrableOn
      (fun П„ => petersson k
        ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) вҲЈ[k]
          peterssonAdj Оұ) вҮ‘g П„)
      (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ)) Ој_hyp)
    (h_FD_balance :
      peterssonInner k
        (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f))
        ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g)) вҲЈ[k]
          peterssonAdj Оұ) =
      peterssonInner k
        (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
        ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) вҲЈ[k]
          peterssonAdj Оұ) вҮ‘g) :
    (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f) вҲЈ[k]
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g) вҲЈ[k]
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) =
    вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) вҲЈ[k]
          ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
        (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) := by
  -- Step 1: LHS aggregate via peterssonInner_sum_slash_adjoint_coset_aggregate.
  have h_LHS_agg := peterssonInner_sum_slash_adjoint_coset_aggregate
    (k := k) Оұ hОұ
    (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f))
    (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g))
    hd hm hint_LHS
  -- Step 2: RHS aggregate via per-q `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset_right`
  -- + `peterssonInner_iUnion_finite_aedisjoint`.
  have h_RHS_agg :
      (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) вҲЈ[k]
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
          (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
            (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))) =
      peterssonInner k
        (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
        ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) вҲЈ[k]
          peterssonAdj Оұ) вҮ‘g := by
    rw [show (вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) вҲЈ[k]
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
          (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k]
            (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))) =
      вҲ‘ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        peterssonInner k
          ((Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
          ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) вҲЈ[k]
            peterssonAdj Оұ) вҮ‘g from by
      refine Finset.sum_congr rfl fun q _ => ?_
      rw [peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset_right (k := k) Оұ hОұ
        (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))
        вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) вҮ‘g, вҶҗ mul_smul]]
    exact (peterssonInner_iUnion_finite_aedisjoint
      (fun q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N =>
        (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
      hm hd
      ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj Оұ)
      вҮ‘g hint_RHS).symm
  -- Combine: balanced_LHS = LHS_agg = (h_FD_balance) = RHS_agg = balanced_RHS.
  rw [h_LHS_agg, h_FD_balance, вҶҗ h_RHS_agg]

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T090 slash-adjoint sub-reduction of `h_FD_balance`.**

Reduces the aggregate-FD-balance hypothesis (consumed by
`balanced_Оұ_of_aggregate_FD_balance`) to a **post-swap** form on
the same union domain `U_Оұ := вӢғ_q (Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd`, with the
`peterssonAdj Оұ` factor moved off the slot-2/slot-1 g-side via two
applications of slash-adjoint (`peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_right`
on the LHS, `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint` on the RHS), with positivity
of `(peterssonAdj Оұ).det` from `peterssonAdj_det`, and the
double-adjoint collapse `peterssonAdj_peterssonAdj`:

```
peterssonInner k (peterssonAdj Оұ вҖў U_Оұ) ((вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©f) вҲЈ Оұ) (вҹЁuвҒ»В№вҹ©g)
  = peterssonInner k (peterssonAdj Оұ вҖў U_Оұ) (вҹЁuвҹ©f) (g вҲЈ Оұ)
```

This is the **post-swap form**: integrals over `peterssonAdj Оұ вҖў U_Оұ`
of petersson kernels with Оұ applied directly (not via `peterssonAdj`).

**Use site.** Discharging this post-swap balance hypothesis discharges the
original `h_FD_balance` consumed by `balanced_Оұ_of_aggregate_FD_balance`,
hence the entire FD slash-exchange / tile-shift residual chain.

**Next step toward closure.** The domain `peterssonAdj Оұ вҖў U_Оұ` further
simplifies via `peterssonAdj Оұ В· Оұ = (det Оұ) В· 1` (matrix algebra:
`Matrix.adjugate_mul`) and the trivial action of scalar matrices on
`UpperHalfPlane` вҖ” collapsing to the standard SL-tile union
`вӢғ_q (mapGL q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd` (= the О“вӮҒ(N) fundamental domain at SL level).
The remaining identity is then a Petersson-integral balance over the
canonical О“вӮҒ(N) fundamental domain, eligible for discharge via
`petN_slash_invariant` / `diamondOp_petersson_unitary`. -/
private theorem h_FD_balance_of_post_swap_balance
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) (hОұ : 0 < Оұ.det.val)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k)
    (h_post_swap_balance :
      peterssonInner k
        (peterssonAdj Оұ вҖў вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
        ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f)) вҲЈ[k] Оұ)
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g)) =
      peterssonInner k
        (peterssonAdj Оұ вҖў вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f))
        (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] Оұ)) :
    peterssonInner k
      (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
      (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f))
      ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g)) вҲЈ[k]
        peterssonAdj Оұ) =
    peterssonInner k
      (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
        (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
          (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
      ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) вҲЈ[k]
        peterssonAdj Оұ) вҮ‘g := by
  -- positive determinant of peterssonAdj Оұ (= Оұ.det)
  have hОұ_adj : 0 < (peterssonAdj Оұ).det.val := by
    show 0 < ((peterssonAdj Оұ).det : в„қЛЈ).val
    rw [peterssonAdj_det]
    exact hОұ
  -- Apply peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_right to LHS.
  rw [peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_right
        (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
        (peterssonAdj Оұ) hОұ_adj
        вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f)
        вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g),
      peterssonAdj_peterssonAdj]
  -- Apply peterssonInner_slash_adjoint to RHS.
  rw [peterssonInner_slash_adjoint
        (вӢғ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
          (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            (q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
        (peterssonAdj Оұ) hОұ_adj
        вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f) вҮ‘g,
      peterssonAdj_peterssonAdj]
  exact h_post_swap_balance

open UpperHalfPlane in
/-- **T090 trivial action of `peterssonAdj ОІ В· ОІ` on a point of `в„Қ`.**

The matrix product `peterssonAdj ОІ В· ОІ` equals the scalar matrix `(det ОІ) В· 1`
(by `Matrix.adjugate_mul`), and positive scalar matrices act trivially on
`UpperHalfPlane` via MГ¶bius. Proof here is via the GL group structure:
`peterssonAdj ОІ вҖў П„ = ОІвҒ»В№ вҖў П„` (by `peterssonAdj_smul_eq`, the `peterssonAdj`
acts as the inverse on `в„Қ`), so
`(peterssonAdj ОІ * ОІ) вҖў П„ = peterssonAdj ОІ вҖў ОІ вҖў П„ = ОІвҒ»В№ вҖў ОІ вҖў П„ = П„`. -/
private lemma peterssonAdj_mul_self_smul
    (ОІ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) (П„ : в„Қ) :
    ((peterssonAdj ОІ * ОІ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў П„ : в„Қ) = П„ := by
  rw [mul_smul, peterssonAdj_smul_eq, inv_smul_smul]

open UpperHalfPlane in
/-- **T090 trivial action of `peterssonAdj ОІ В· ОІ` on sets of `в„Қ`.**

Set-level extension of `peterssonAdj_mul_self_smul`: pointwise triviality
implies `(peterssonAdj ОІ В· ОІ) вҖў S = S` for any `S : Set в„Қ`. -/
lemma peterssonAdj_mul_self_smul_set
    (ОІ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) (S : Set в„Қ) :
    ((peterssonAdj ОІ * ОІ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў S : Set в„Қ) = S := by
  ext П„
  refine вҹЁ?_, ?_вҹ©
  В· rintro вҹЁs, hs, hП„вҹ©
    -- hП„ has the form (fun x => _ вҖў x) s = П„; cast to action form
    have hП„' : (peterssonAdj ОІ * ОІ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў s = П„ := hП„
    rw [peterssonAdj_mul_self_smul] at hП„'
    exact hП„' в–ё hs
  В· intro hП„
    refine вҹЁП„, hП„, ?_вҹ©
    show (peterssonAdj ОІ * ОІ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў П„ = П„
    exact peterssonAdj_mul_self_smul ОІ П„

open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
