/-- **LHS-aggregate-as-tile-form with per-ОІ g-slot identifications**.

Refinement of `petN_heckeT_p_LHS_as_tile_aggregate` that applies the per-ОІ
adjugate slash identifications to the g-slot:

- For ОІ = `glMap T_p_upper(b)`:
  `вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj ОІ = вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] glMap T_p_lower` (independent of `b`!)
  via `slash_peterssonAdj_T_p_upper_eq_T_p_lower`.

- For ОІ = `glMap M_вҲһ`:
