  `вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] peterssonAdj ОІ = (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] glMap T_p_upper(0)) вҲЈ[k] mapGL в„қ Пғ_pвҒ»В№`
  via `peterssonAdj_glMap_M_infty_eq` + `SlashAction.slash_mul`.

