`petersson k вҮ‘f (вҮ‘g вҲЈ[k] glMap T_p_lower)`. Summing over `b` therefore
collapses to integration over the union `вӢғ_b T_p_upper(b) вҖў (q.outвҒ»В№ вҖў fd)`,
