/-- **T090 / T205 strict reducer: M_вҲһ branch of `heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance`
from a per-tile slot-swap identity.**

Aggregates a per-tile (per-`q вҲҲ SL(2,в„Ө) в§ё О“вӮҒ(N)`) M_вҲһ slot-swap identity
`h_per_tile` into the **M_вҲһ branch** of
`heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance` (i.e. `h_canon.1`), via
`peterssonInner_iUnion_finite_aedisjoint`.

