`h_per_tile q` is the slot-swap identity `(fвҲЈM_вҲһ, g) = (f, gвҲЈM_вҲһ)`
restricted to a *single* SL-tile `(mapGL q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd`, whereas the
aggregate hypothesis (the M_вҲһ branch of `heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance`)
is the same identity over the *union* of all such tiles
