open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T090 / T205 strict reducer: per-tile slot-swap from per-q FD-form balance.**

Pulls back the per-tile slot-swap identity (over the SL-tile
`(mapGL q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd`) to the per-q FD-form balance (over `fd`) via
`peterssonInner_mapGL_smul_eq_slash`.  This pushes one layer deeper
than `heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance_Оұ_branch_from_per_tile_balance`:
the SL-tile domain is converted to fd via the SL change-of-variables,
folding the integration shift into the integrand slashes.

**Strictly smaller hypothesis.** The per-q FD-form balance
`h_per_q_fd q` is a single equality of integrals over a *fixed* domain
(`fd`), with the SL-tile shift absorbed into the slash composition
`Оұ * (mapGL q.outвҒ»В№)` on the f-slot and `mapGL q.outвҒ»В№` alone on the
g-slot.  The per-tile form has the *shifted* domain `(mapGL q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd`
but a simpler integrand pair (`f вҲЈ Оұ, g`).

**Why this is a real reduction, not repackaging.** The proof body
applies the SL-pullback identity `peterssonInner_mapGL_smul_eq_slash`
on each side of the per-tile equation, then folds the resulting
nested slashes `(F вҲЈ Оұ) вҲЈ (mapGL q.outвҒ»В№) = F вҲЈ (Оұ * mapGL q.outвҒ»В№)`
via `SlashAction.slash_mul`.  Both steps are non-trivial helpers, not
mere renaming.

**Proof structure.**
1. `intro q`.
2. Apply `peterssonInner_mapGL_smul_eq_slash` on each side (LHS and RHS):
   converts `peterssonInner k ((mapGL q.outвҒ»В№) вҖў fd) F G` to
   `peterssonInner k fd (F вҲЈ mapGL q.outвҒ»В№) (G вҲЈ mapGL q.outвҒ»В№)`.
3. Fold the slot-1 slashes `((F вҲЈ Оұ) вҲЈ mapGL q.outвҒ»В№)` to
   `F вҲЈ (Оұ * mapGL q.outвҒ»В№)` via `вҶҗ SlashAction.slash_mul`.
4. Apply `h_per_q_fd q`. -/
private theorem heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance_Оұ_branch_per_tile_from_per_q_fd_balance
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k)
    (h_per_q_fd : вҲҖ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f)) вҲЈ[k]
            (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
          ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g)) вҲЈ[k]
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) =
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) вҲЈ[k]
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
          ((вҮ‘g) вҲЈ[k]
            (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))) :
    вҲҖ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k
          (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ))
          ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f)) вҲЈ[k] Оұ)
