open UpperHalfPlane ModularGroup MeasureTheory in
/-- **T090 / T205 strict reducer: per-q FD-form balance from shifted-tile
diamond/slot swap (single named genuine analytic content).**

Reduces the per-q FD-form Оұ-slot-swap (consumed by
`Оұ_branch_per_tile_from_per_q_fd_balance`) to a **single named genuine
analytic identity**: the **shifted-tile diamond/slot swap residual**

  `peterssonInner k (Оұ вҖў q.outвҒ»В№ вҖў fd) (вҹЁpвҹ©вҒ»В№f) ((вҹЁpвҹ©вҒ»В№g) вҲЈ peterssonAdj Оұ)
    = peterssonInner k (Оұ вҖў q.outвҒ»В№ вҖў fd) ((вҹЁpвҹ©f) вҲЈ peterssonAdj Оұ) g`

вҖ” a per-`q` Petersson identity over the *same* shifted-tile domain
`Оұ вҖў q.outвҒ»В№ вҖў fd`, with the diamond `вҹЁpвҹ©` вҶ” `вҹЁpвҹ©вҒ»В№` swap and the slot
swap (slot-1 вҶ” slot-2) absorbing each other across `peterssonAdj Оұ`.

**Why this is the irreducible analytic core (manager hint #2:
"diamond-twisted slash-invariance theorem strong enough to move Оұ
between Petersson slots over fd").**  Both sides have IDENTICAL slash
compositions on slot-i where Оұ appears (just `peterssonAdj Оұ`), with
the only difference being:
* slot-1: `вҹЁpвҹ©вҒ»В№f` (LHS) vs `(вҹЁpвҹ©f) вҲЈ peterssonAdj Оұ` (RHS) вҖ” diamond-twist + slash-by-Оұ swap;
* slot-2: `(вҹЁpвҹ©вҒ»В№g) вҲЈ peterssonAdj Оұ` (LHS) vs `g` (RHS) вҖ” diamond-twist + slash-by-Оұ swap.

The `q.outвҒ»В№` factor of the original slash composition `Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№` has
been absorbed into the integration domain via SL change-of-variables;
the genuine per-q content thereby reduces to the diamond-twisted
slot-swap of the Petersson kernel for `Оұ` against itself, evaluated on
the SL-tile.

**Proof structure.**
1. `intro q`.
2. Apply `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset` (ОІ := Оұ, q := q.out) on
   LHS_target: the slash composition `(Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№)` is absorbed via
   change-of-variables to give an integral over `Оұ вҖў q.outвҒ»В№ вҖў fd` with
   slot-2 carrying `peterssonAdj Оұ`.
3. Apply `peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset_right` (ОІ := Оұ, q := q.out)
   on RHS_target: the slash composition `(Оұ В· q.outвҒ»В№)` on the
   slot-2 of `g` is absorbed, putting `peterssonAdj Оұ` on slot-1.
4. Apply `h_shifted q` to close the residual.

This is uniform in Оұ, so the same theorem covers both M_вҲһ and
T_p_upper(b) Hecke representatives. -/
private theorem heckeFD_canonical_SL_tile_balance_Оұ_branch_per_q_fd_from_shifted_tile_diamond_swap
    (Оұ : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) (hОұ : 0 < Оұ.det.val)
    (p : в„•) (hp : Nat.Prime p) (hpN : Nat.Coprime p N)
    (f g : CuspForm ((Gamma1 N).map (mapGL в„қ)) k)
    (h_shifted : вҲҖ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k
          (Оұ вҖў (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ)))
          (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f))
          ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g)) вҲЈ[k]
            peterssonAdj Оұ) =
      peterssonInner k
          (Оұ вҖў (((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
            ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ) вҖў (fd : Set в„Қ)))
          ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) вҲЈ[k]
            peterssonAdj Оұ)
          вҮ‘g) :
    вҲҖ q : SL(2, в„Ө) в§ё Gamma1 N,
      peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f)) вҲЈ[k]
            (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)))
          ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g)) вҲЈ[k]
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ)) =
        peterssonInner k ModularGroup.fd
          ((вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f)) вҲЈ[k]
            ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))
          ((вҮ‘g) вҲЈ[k]
            (Оұ * ((mapGL в„қ : SL(2, в„Ө) вҶ’* GL (Fin 2) в„қ)
              ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө))вҒ»В№) : GL (Fin 2) в„қ))) := by
  intro q
  rw [peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset (k := k) Оұ hОұ ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө)))
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ f))
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN)вҒ»В№ g))]
  rw [peterssonInner_slash_adjoint_coset_right (k := k) Оұ hОұ ((q.out : SL(2, в„Ө)))
        (вҮ‘(diamondOp_cusp k (ZMod.unitOfCoprime p hpN) f))
        (вҮ‘g)]
  exact h_shifted q

